data.title: Fake My Feelings (feat. Torine)
data.meta_description: Norwegian singer/songwriter Ponette has announced she'll be releasing her second album later this year titled "Part I" and this week...
data.text:
Norwegian singer/songwriter Ponette has announced she’ll be releasing her second album later this year titled “Part I” and this week she’s giving us a little taste of what we can except with the vibrant indie/alt-pop sounds of new single ‘Fake My Feelings’, which also has her working with fellow Norwegian artist Torine to help bring this one to life.

Ponette’s first release of 2023 was a song called ‘Beats Me Up’ which was a collaboration with another Norwegian artist who goes by the name Coucheron, and that one is also very much worthy of a few listens – which you can do so right here
